<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 offset-md-3">
      <div class="row text-center card my-3 px-4 border p-3">

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-8 offset-2 col-md-6 offset-md-3">
            <script src="https://unpkg.com/@lottiefiles/lottie-player@latest/dist/lottie-player.js"></script>
            <lottie-player class="webpay-loader" src="https://assets6.lottiefiles.com/packages/lf20_clztx5wi.json" background="transparent" speed="1" style="width: 300px; height: 220px;margin: 0 auto;" loop autoplay></lottie-player>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <h6 class="sans-serif mb-3 mt-0">Te llevaremos a Webpay para agregar tu nueva tarjeta</h6>
            <p style="font-size: .8rem;">Al ingresa los datos se efectuar√° un cobro de $50 pesos para confirmar tu tarjeta.</p>
            <p style="font-size: .8rem;">Luego regresaremos a Lomi para termminar tu compra.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">

          <div class="col-12 col-md-10 offset-md-1">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-6">
                <%= link_to Spree.t("back"), checkout_state_path(:payment), class: "btn btn-info w-100 btn-outline-primary white" %>
              </div>
              <div class="col-6">
                <%= form_for :subscribe, url: oneclick_mall_subscribe_path do |f| %>
                  <%= f.hidden_field  :back_url, value: request.referer %>
                  <%= f.submit 'Ir a Webpay', class: "btn btn-primary  w-100 " %>
                <% end %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>